# .cursor/rules/solana-wallet.rule
# ------------------------------------------------------------------
# 코딩 스타일
Always write browser-compatible ES2020 JavaScript in strict mode.
Use functional, immutable patterns where reasonable.

# 문서화
Add Korean JSDoc comments for every public function.

# 테스트
Write Vitest unit tests first; ensure tests pass before final code.

# 에러 처리
Wrap external-call errors in try/catch and return Result objects
instead of throwing raw errors.

# 번들
Assume Vite with vite-plugin-node-polyfills is configured so that
Buffer, process 등 Node 전역이 브라우저에서도 동작한다.

# 출력 형식
When modifying code, output the *entire* file content unless asked
for 'patch' format. Include all imports at top of file.

# 불필요한 설명 최소화
Keep AI responses concise—focus on code, not prose.
